short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Session Replay browser extension that allows to proxy loading of resources when replaying a session.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhances session playback, especially when:
 * Font and stylesheet resources are loaded from HTTPS origins
 * Resources are loaded from HTTP origins
